TRADEMARK raced two wide off the pace, three wide on the backside, moved up five wide at the quarter pole, rallied outside in the stretch and got up for third. ARTORIUS raced three wide early, stalked close up two wide, vied two wide on the backside, dueled between rivals on the far turn, dug in gamely in the two path in the stretch. BOURBONIC raced four wide on the first turn, moved up four wide on the backside to contest the pace, chased four wide on the far turn, came five wide into the lane and finished evenly. OCTANE set the pace on the inside, vied inside on the backside, dueled on the far turn and weakened in the final furlong. BOURBON CALLING broke a step slow, raced off the rail, off the pace and did not factor. EMPTY TOMB raced off the pace inside, moved up on the backside, chased on the far turn and faded.

RACE.FOOTNOTES: CATNIP raced three wide in the chute, then stalked close up two wide, was shuffled back some entering the far turn, continued between rivals on the turn, came two wide into the lane, angled out, rallied outside in midstretch, surged outside rivals past the sixteenth marker and closed strongly for the win. NEVER EXPLAIN raced off the pace between rivals, pulled his way into contention with a four wide middle move on the backside, bid two wide on the far turn, rallied to a short lead, edged clear in midstretch and then dug in gamely to the finish. SPEAKING SCOUT trailed on the inside, made a five wide middle move outside of NEVER EXPLAIN, tracked three wide on the far turn, rallied outside, made a late bid between rivals and was outkicked. TRIBHUVAN (FR) set the pace on the inside, showed the way into the far turn, dueled inside passing the quarter pole, dug in and then weakened. COMMANDEER raced three wide early, then stalked three wide, was shuffled back a bit entering the far turn, continued three wide and lacked a rally. DYNADRIVE tracked along the inside, chased inside on the far turn and had no rally.
